735
00:45:47.666 --> 00:45:49.541
- [suspenseful music resumes]
- [expels breath]

736
00:45:52.291 --> 00:45:53.833
[in Sotho] I'm sorry. Ndumiso.

737
00:45:55.625 --> 00:45:57.166
[in English] You'd still be alive

738
00:45:58.541 --> 00:46:00.000
if I'd never met you.

739
00:46:02.125 --> 00:46:03.125
[sniffles]

740
00:46:04.041 --> 00:46:06.166
[sobs] I hope that you know

741
00:46:06.750 --> 00:46:08.125
that I loved you.

742
00:46:10.125 --> 00:46:12.291
[voice breaks]
I loved you so much. Ndumiso.

743
00:46:19.208 --> 00:46:21.208
[music intensifies]

744
00:46:24.291 --> 00:46:25.666
[gasps and screams]

745
00:46:28.666 --> 00:46:30.708
[music fades]

746
00:46:33.166 --> 00:46:34.666
[dramatic sting]

747
00:46:37.875 --> 00:46:39.875
[dramatic music plays]

748
00:46:53.583 --> 00:46:54.583
[music stops]

749
00:46:57.291 --> 00:46:59.291
[dramatic instrumental music plays]

750
00:47:45.333 --> 00:47:47.708
[music fades]
